OL,5, More than a dozen sub-postmasters and  
OL,6, postmistresses who were victims of     
OL,7, armed robberies were told to pay back  
OL,8, the stolen money, the BBC has heard.   
OL,10,FOne said the Post Office wanted him to 
OL,11,Fpay back #2,000 that robbers had       
OL,12,Fstolen, after it spent five years      
OL,13,Frefusing to upgrade his security.      
OL,15,FBBC Newsnight knows of 15 others who   
OL,16,Fexperienced similar treatment, six of  
OL,17,Fwhom have spoken directly about it.    
OL,19,FThe Post Office said it had            
OL,20,Fsignificantly enhanced victim support. 
